Module count
Package count.model

Class MLPhylogeny.CandidateMove

java.lang.Object
count.model.MLPhylogeny.CandidateMove
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<MLPhylogeny.CandidateMove>
Enclosing class:
MLPhylogeny
private class MLPhylogeny.CandidateMove
extends Object
implements Comparable<MLPhylogeny.CandidateMove>
Candidate moves: SPR (join), edge contraction, and rerooting. The score variable serves to cache the ML score (set externally}, and the model rates is set if it is optimized by either scoreFastML(int) or scoreML(int). version serves to catch the updates to the reference model. Accepting a candidate move updates the reference model, and increases its version. New SPR moves are instanciated by the join(int, int), contract(int) and reroot(int) methods.
Author:
csuros
